  <div class="container">
    <div class="block__content split">
      <div class="block-icon-container">{{>icon name="award" class="awards-icon"}}</div>
      <h2 class="h2 text-center">The two Manchester Homelessness Partnership standards are:</h2>
      <div class="split__element split__element--highlight">
        <h3 class="h2 text-center split__element--title">Silver Best Practice</h3>
        <p>To be eligible to receive the standard for Silver Best Practice, your organisation must have:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Offer a reliable and responsible service</li>
          <li>Support the aims of Manchester Homelessness Charter</li>
          <li>A group leader with a current <a href="https://www.gov.uk/disclosure-barring-service-check/overview">DBS check</a></li>
          <li>Public liability insurance</li>
          <li>Safeguarding policy</li>
          <li>Volunteer policy</li>
          <li>Health and safety policy</li>
          <li>Confidentiality policy</li>
          <li>Social media usage policy</li>
          <li>Financial policy and organisation bank account</li>
          <li>Engage with COR or an established organisation</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="split__element split__element--highlight">
        <h3 class="h2 text-center split__element--title">Gold Best Practice</h3>
        <p>To receive the standard for Gold Best Practice, your organisation must have:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>All Commended Best Practice standards in place.</li>
          <li>A volunteer induction process, including application form, reference and id checks</li>
          <li>Lone working policy</li>
          <li>Volunteer policy</li>
          <li>Blood borne diseases policy</li>
          <li>Data protection policy</li>
          <li>A DBS checked volunteer present at all times</li>
        <ul>
      </div>
    </div>
